#

Chicken Piccata

35 min
$12
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-Free OptionHigh Protein

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

ItalianQuick MealComfort Food

Description

A flavorful Italian dish featuring tender chicken breasts in a lemony caper sauce, served over pasta or with a side of vegetables.

Ingredients

  • chicken breasts: 2, boneless and skinless
  • all-purpose flour: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • chicken broth: 1/2 cup
  • lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • capers: 2 tablespoons, drained
  • parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
